How to use your Moodlight in 6 easy steps

1. Compile the software:
	make

2. Set your Moodlight to programming mode by holding the HWB button and pressing the RESET button.

3. Erase the old binary from your Moodlight (may require root privilege):
	dfu-programmer atmega32u2 erase

4. Flash the new binary onto your Moodlight (may require root privilege):
	dfu-programmer atmega32u2 flash Moodlight.hex 

5. Reset your Moodlight by pressing the RESET button.

6. Tell your Moodlight to blink for you (see readme in ../host/HidCom)	
